text: Gonçalo Óscar Albuquerque Borges (born 29 March 2001) is a Portuguese professional footballer who plays for FC Porto B as a forward. ==Football career== He made his LigaPro debut for Porto B on 11 August 2019 in a game against Sporting Covilhã. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:2001 births Category:Portuguese footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:LigaPro players Category:FC Porto B players Category:Living people
